~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
* Support elasticsearch-dsl>6.3.0
* Class `Meta` has changed to class `Django` (See PR #136)
* Add `register_document` decorator to register a document (See PR #136)
* Additional Bug fixing and others


